	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salve, vir optime.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ultimas tuas accepi cum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749" cert="high">Saxonicis</placeName>; placuerunt, sed utinam non tam cruda essent, imo ampliora.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3375" cert="high">Vergerius</persName> fuit <placeName ref="l491" cert="high">Argentinę</placeName>, unde mihi scripsit tibique, ut videbis ex iis, que mitto.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nova a me expectas ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italia</placeName>; habuisti a domino consule Hab, que venere tempore comitiorum.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iam audies etiam, que ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2589" cert="high">Picardia</placeName>; scribo enim dominis omnia.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Thyrannus ille, si quid cordi habeat, deberet sufocari et tamen vivit in christianę reipublicę perniciem.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Filius, quidquid iactetur, nondum est in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod ad vestram rempublicam, audieris a vestris legatis, quo in statu sint ea, de quibus antea scripsimus.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Video omnia pacifica.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus vestris statibus adsit.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iam isti <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l631" cert="high">Burgundi</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Almani</placeName> multi et Caesariani ridebant scribebantque, nunc publice recitabunt Helvetios pugnare civilibusque bellis agitari et esse spem, quod Caesar alteri parti vellet auxilium ferre.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Di boni, qualia monstra.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De iis vester consul poterit amplius communicare.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Illum saluto teque.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale, vir optime etc.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l760" cert="high">Soluturo</placeName> raptim 5a iulii.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus semper <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8296" cert="high">Bass[afontaneus]</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse fehlt.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
